{"tid":433991,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"グレープ君 10月21日離世 享年21","createTime":"2017-10-13T00:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T07:45:31.000Z","uid":7307,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2c13ba79b5ee623f8e89ebcb9317408540deeef5","tid":433991,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/085913_49448ee396e8dbcb7191fccea6de82ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F085913_49448ee396e8dbcb7191fccea6de82ae.jpg&h=d3a0e0cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nフンボルトペンギンのグレープ君が昨日亡くなりました。<br />\nこれまで応援してくれた皆様本当にありがとうございました。また、グレープ君を最後まで見守ってくれたフルルもありがとう。そして、グレープ君長い間ありがとう。天国でゆっくり休んでね。#東武動物公園  #けものフレンズ  #グレープ君<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tobuzoo7/status/918633438919368704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftobuzoo7%2Fstatus%2F918633438919368704&d=88pLlQRtdcCMvbw0s3jR4ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=9018b7b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftobuzoo7%2Fstatus%2F918633438919368704&h=16c9c884\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tobuzoo7/status/918633438919368704</a>"},{"pid":"44bc6829beb506f2b7d13509f7377696f6efbe7c","tid":433991,"uid":69546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:45:16.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20eb48d1260a05b3bb1c37864ba5b2239d72201a","tid":433991,"uid":96983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T03:50:47.000Z","msg":"10月21日都未到<br />\n寫左死亡筆記呀?"},{"pid":"08eb6f3d9625289ae14e1a8fcc3c4c0a0ed1ca8f","tid":433991,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T04:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10月21日都未到<br />\n寫左死亡筆記呀?</blockquote><br />\n打錯左<br />\n12"},{"pid":"faf9a355301b201663f8de8dd51039d1af1dbb27","tid":433991,"uid":35